{"tid":2094748,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九東5泛民堅拒簽確認書  黃之鋒：增政權DQ成本 譚得志：不為入閘食屎","createTime":"2020-07-05T02:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T10:16:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"58cbe2fc7c4eb8fabd91d6b74ef1c67dd6363ab6","tid":2094748,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:38:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/YGX2OMF7TER74HWBJOCRXNN6XY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2FYGX2OMF7TER74HWBJOCRXNN6XY%2F&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmh68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=6ff6c0bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200705%2FYGX2OMF7TER74HWBJOCRXNN6XY%2F&h=9d2bfa73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200705/YGX2OMF7TER74HWBJOCRXNN6XY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n九東5泛民堅拒簽確認書 <br />\n黃之鋒：增政權DQ成本 譚得志：不為入閘食屎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/frnJy5yxfEdVunUbPxlYiQzVhzI=/638x720/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R5AUU4YBENXX5OKJKPCRQ5XBDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfrnJy5yxfEdVunUbPxlYiQzVhzI%3D%2F638x720%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR5AUU4YBENXX5OKJKPCRQ5XBDQ.jpg&h=2ffbcc59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒堅決不會簽署任何支持國安法的文件。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法規定，港人參選或就任公職時應簽署文件確認或宣誓擁<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n公民黨譚文豪則表示未有決定，但若然市民期望所有民主派候選人拒簽確認書，他亦不會簽。<br />\n<br />\n各參選人在論壇上被問到確認書若加入支持國安法條文，會否因為入閘而簽署。黃之鋒率先指，他忠誠反對國安法，故不會簽署任何支持國安法的文件，又建議民主派候選人一同拒簽確認書，增加政權DQ參選人的成本：「堅定嘅抵抗意志係香港需要見到，而今次初選投票亦都係讓政權知道香港人未投降。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KaAfJeuBqT5GTmeRHzt8_f48yCU=/190x133/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ITXM5HHIVHCHLGBSLTUKORAIEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKaAfJeuBqT5GTmeRHzt8_f48yCU%3D%2F190x133%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FITXM5HHIVHCHLGBSLTUKORAIEQ.jpg&h=9d6d4da5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施德來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0rl9FHe_EZEPxbT3C3wAGFsMVXA=/640x465/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IXF5A6MPAEUABCLHFYGXRVNGMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0rl9FHe_EZEPxbT3C3wAGFsMVXA%3D%2F640x465%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIXF5A6MPAEUABCLHFYGXRVNGMU.jpg&h=a55aed3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李嘉達<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉：Plan B須爭入閘<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：職員指覆檢大量書籍從未見 或歷時半年<br />\n<br />\n現任議員胡志偉分析，<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n；但胡認為民主派Plan B的參選人則要不惜一切入閘。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉達同樣認為，任何在立法會議員當選宣誓前的確認書都是不必要，指議員當選後會宣誓效忠《基本法》，他亦呼籲全港的民主派參選人都不要簽署確認書。譚得志亦指，人民力量過去未有簽署確認書，今次選舉也堅決拒簽：「呢個就係我哋嘅抗爭意志&hellip;&hellip;我哋嘅底線究竟去到邊度？係咪有得入閘就屎都食？呢嚿屎我哋絕對食唔落。」民協施德來斥，今次的確認書是「加料版」，民協不會簽署，若政府因此而DQ所有民主派參選人，也讓國際社會有更好理由制裁中共。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IUO3JUZtvkfnCXb4g4FDB4hk73A=/190x142/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X6B24MSBYQ7BZJYBRFPD35GH7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIUO3JUZtvkfnCXb4g4FDB4hk73A%3D%2F190x142%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX6B24MSBYQ7BZJYBRFPD35GH7Y.jpg&h=2d292640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚得志<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/A6DCXfT4vM8QuGNUF17QdoxgYFs=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IOFMOEMPHKXOUPNAD74SOTRDIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FA6DCXfT4vM8QuGNUF17QdoxgYFs%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIOFMOEMPHKXOUPNAD74SOTRDIA.jpg&h=c3ca80ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡志偉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪︰視乎市民意見<br />\n<br />\n公民黨譚文豪初時未就確認書表態，稱確認書已經成為DQ參選人的條件，質疑「如果我哋全部都入唔到閘嘅話，又如何做得成35+呢？最後一個人都入唔到閘嘅時候，係咪市民想見到嘅35+？」他之後補充，「若然香港人接受到唔簽（確認書），放棄35+，我會做。」<br />\n<br />\n不過他們在民主派Plan B是否要不惜一切入閘則未有共識，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n到成個立法會都係建制派」。"},{"pid":"595882d3a7454c00c2ea0018422a88009166bab5","tid":2094748,"uid":113074,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"國安法已經降臨，<br />\n行出銅鑼灣仲要聽班政棍講35+有用同籌款<br />\n真係屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7fed2bd75ec07a95a5546dd374cbd4addcb70d","tid":2094748,"uid":231583,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"35+就係博佢DQ增加管治成本推動制裁，根本都唔會奪到權<br />\nPlan A B都根本唔應該簽，比你過到呢關，入到去投反對票咪一樣再DQ你囉"},{"pid":"ea9d9a36f81140d7ce43d976e8ed7eb125371eb7","tid":2094748,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:57:23.000Z","msg":"有國安法底下,如果35+<br />\n投票反對政府任何議案<br />\n<br />\n跟據第二十二條，嚴重干擾、阻撓、破壞中華人民共和國政權機關或香港特別行政區機關依法履行職能<br />\n<br />\n其實都已經干犯國安法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab2ce9d908ed43127f4e90892fa843baa9101f1","tid":2094748,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"你plan b 簽 人地咪拎住你個名話民主黨都支持國安法<br />\n有無咁撚蠢呀 而家唔係以前支持基本法 <br />\n而家講緊係國安法呀"},{"pid":"b8b9ad37e45341e688096491a385838993922189","tid":2094748,"uid":150610,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"今日退五步，明日退十步，然後獲得一席安寢"},{"pid":"83ca70ff7d0c7eb14545fd250caaa480eaf549d3","tid":2094748,"uid":331421,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-